{
  "_comment": "Podcast Production Engine :: intake mapper alias + enum tables (webhook-design.md Section 4.2). Data-driven so onboarding can extend a client's pipeline aliases without a code change. Fuzzy matching strips every non-alphanumeric character and lowercases both sides, so 'Contact-ID', 'contact id', and 'ContactId' all converge; the tables below are read for their MEANING, never their exact spelling. The GHL survey field keys whose internal labels are Barry/Brene/Dan/Jia Q-numbers are supplied per client at onboarding via survey_answer_keys_by_style (positional, by the chosen style path); those internal labels never appear in any output.",
